attempts.sparql_query: PREFIX atm: <https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/ATM#> PREFIX nas: <https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/NAS#> SELECT?arrivalDayCHQ2945?arrivalDayAAL1102 WHERE { atm:CHQ2945-201407150047 atm:actualArrivalDay?arrivalDayCHQ2945. atm:AAL1102-201407150046 atm:actualArrivalDay?arrivalDayAAL1102. }
attempts.query_explanation: This SPARQL query retrieves the actual arrival days of flights CHQ2945 and AAL1102. The query uses the atm:actualArrivalDay property to link the flights to their respective arrival days. The results will show the arrival days for both flights, allowing us to determine if they arrived on the same day.
